====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# {{senseid|en|wager}} A [[wager]], an agreement between two parties that a stake (usually money) will be paid by the loser to the winner (the winner being the one who correctly forecast the outcome of an event).
#: ''Dylan owes Fletcher $30 from an unsuccessful '''bet.'''''
# A degree of [[certainty]].
#: ''It’s a safe '''bet''' that it will rain tomorrow.''
#: ''It’s an even '''bet''' that Jim will come top of the maths test tomorrow''

